120
00:06:35,810 --> 00:06:37,660
Dia telah diambil
ke balai polis dengan Hongbing.

121
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:38,920
Dia memakai ini apabila dia kembali.

122
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,100
Ini adalah pakaiannya.

123
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,500
awak cakap apa?

124
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:46,540
Bilakah Hui

125
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:48,340
dibawa ke stesen oleh Hongbing?

126
00:06:48,340 --> 00:06:49,490
Minggu lepas,

127
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:50,490
pada hari lahir anda.

128
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:53,100
Hui memanggil Songge.

129
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:54,570
Saya mendengarnya.

130
00:06:55,490 --> 00:06:56,780
Pada hari lahir saya?

131
00:06:57,930 --> 00:06:58,770
Ia

132
00:06:59,490 --> 00:07:00,660
adalah hari selepas kami makan kek.

133
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:05,140
Hui juga memberitahu saya ketika itu

134
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,340
bukan untuk memberitahu anda.

135
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,340
Saya cuma lupa.

136
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:11,700
(Senarai Pembelian Komputer)

137
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:13,930
Hui,

138
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:15,490
anda tidak perlu menunjukkan kepada saya

139
00:07:15,490 --> 00:07:16,930
akaun-akaun ini.

140
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:18,100
Beritahu saya

141
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,340
kos akhir.

142
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,980
Encik Huang,

143
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:22,610
kami rakan kongsi.

144
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:23,610
Saya perlu memberitahu anda

145
00:07:23,610 --> 00:07:25,370
semua perbelanjaan kafe internet.

146
00:07:25,370 --> 00:07:27,100
Kami buka esok.

147
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,410
Saya juga mengupah tarian singa

148
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:29,540
untuk membawa kita nasib baik.

149
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:30,810
Tarian singa?

150
00:07:30,810 --> 00:07:32,490
itu hebat.

151
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:34,020
Oh, Hui, selepas awak balik,

152
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:34,930
singgah rumah saya.

153
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:36,220
halau Benz saya.

154
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,100
Anda boleh menggunakannya.

155
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:38,860
Saya tidak memerlukannya.

156
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:40,780
Jika saya meninggalkannya di rumah,

157
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:41,780
tiada siapa boleh memandunya.

158
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,410
Ia hanya akan reput
jika ia duduk di sana terlalu lama.

159
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,170
Anda sentiasa berada di bandar,

160
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:46,050
jadi memandunya

161
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:47,250
akan memberi anda imej yang baik.

162
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,540
Sekurang-kurangnya,

163
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,490
ia berguna untuk mengangkut barang.

164
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,300
Encik Huang,

165
00:07:52,490 --> 00:07:53,330
apa salahnya

166
00:07:53,810 --> 00:07:56,050
Bukan apa. Saya diserang selsema baru-baru ini.

167
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:56,930
Saya telah batuk.

168
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,900
Ini tidak akan berjaya.

169
00:07:58,900 --> 00:07:59,900
Anda perlu berjumpa doktor.

170
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:01,980
Tidak mengapa.

171
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,930
Hanya jangkitan pernafasan.

172
00:08:03,930 --> 00:08:04,970
Saya akan baik dalam beberapa hari.

173
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:08,580
Apa khabar ayah awak?

174
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:11,450
Dia

175
00:08:12,050 --> 00:08:12,890
sedang baik-baik saja.

176
00:08:13,370 --> 00:08:14,490
Ibu saya ada bersamanya.

177
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,410
(Perkakas Rumah Xiaojian)
Bos, saya akan ambil yang ini.

178
00:08:16,410 --> 00:08:17,250
Baiklah.

179
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,490
Datang ambil dalam masa tiga hari.

180
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:22,770
Xiaojian.

181
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,940
Puan Chen, membeli peralatan?

182
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,980
Tidak, saya ingin bertanya sesuatu.

183
00:08:27,370 --> 00:08:28,340
Apa itu?

184
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,180
Teruskan.

185
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:30,900
Adakah anda akan mengambil alih

186
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,340
Gelanggang luncur roller Hui?

187
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,730
Siapa yang beritahu awak?

188
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:34,510
Itu urusannya

189
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,340
ialah awal pagi hingga lewat malam
dan penuh dengan semua jenis orang kasar,

190
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:37,180
jadi saya tidak boleh menanganinya.

191
00:08:39,850 --> 00:08:41,580
Nah, beberapa hari yang lalu,

192
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,530
Hui

193
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:43,460
kembali ke Fengyang.

194
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,300
Adakah kamu berdua minum bersama?

195
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:47,250
Tidak.

196
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:49,770
Sudah tiga atau empat bulan
sejak kali terakhir saya melihat Hui.

197
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,490
apa salahnya

198
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:52,330
Adakah semuanya baik-baik saja?

199
00:08:54,530 --> 00:08:55,370
Bukan apa.

200
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:56,730
Saya hanya bertanya.

201
00:08:58,010 --> 00:08:59,370
Saya akan benarkan awak kembali bekerja.

202
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:00,210
Saya akan pergi sekarang.

203
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:01,690
Jaga diri, Puan Chen.

204
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:06,130
(Yingxiong)
Di manakah saya harus meletakkan ini?

205
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:07,010
Letakkan sahaja di sini.

206
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:08,200
Mercun pergi sini juga.

207
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:09,850
Dah lewat waktu makan.

208
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:10,690
Adakah anda lapar?

209
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:13,220
Dah lama kami lapar.

210
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,940
Jika anda lapar, mengapa anda tidak berkata demikian?

211
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:15,980
Saya fikir awak boleh hidup

212
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:16,850
di udara sahaja.

213
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,340
Sesat.

214
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,890
Saya akan pergi membeli makanan untuk awak.

215
00:09:20,890 --> 00:09:21,820
Terus kemas.

216
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:22,660
Okay.

217
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:26,780
Puan Chen.

218
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:29,850
Liu Ning,

219
00:09:29,850 --> 00:09:30,770
jom pergi.

220
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:33,370
Bagaimana kalau kita pergi membeli makanan itu?

221
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:34,770
Baiklah, mari pergi.

222
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:35,610
Mari pergi, Lei.

223
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,530
- Hello, Puan Chen.
- Hello, Puan Chen.

224
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:40,780
Puan Chen,

225
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:42,420
apa-apa?

226
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,770
Pada malam hari lahir saya,

227
00:09:47,770 --> 00:09:49,130
Hui telah ditangkap oleh ayahnya

228
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:51,100
dan dikurung untuk malam itu.

229
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,060
Adakah anda tahu tentang ini?

230
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:56,610
Songge,

231
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,810
anda tidak pernah berbohong sejak anda kecil.

232
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,420
Awak tak boleh tipu saya.

233
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:01,260
Saya tahu, Puan Chen.

234
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:07,370
