235
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,420
Cuma salah faham pada hari itu.

236
00:10:11,130 --> 00:10:12,010
Encik Chen melepaskannya

237
00:10:12,010 --> 00:10:13,250
keesokan harinya.

238
00:10:13,850 --> 00:10:15,530
Chen Hui cuma takut awak risau,

239
00:10:15,530 --> 00:10:16,980
jadi dia tidak memberitahu anda.

240
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:18,180
Suami saya

241
00:10:19,130 --> 00:10:21,130
telah menjadi polis di Fengyang selama 20 tahun.

242
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:23,340
